Detailed Description

cvmx_ipd_port::_bp_page_cnt3

IPD_PORTX_BP_PAGE_CNT3 = IPD Port Backpressure Page Count The number of pages in use by the port that when exceeded, backpressure will be applied to the port. See also IPD_PORTX_BP_PAGE_CNT See also IPD_PORTX_BP_PAGE_CNT2 0x3d0-408
